<br>
For High Aggro actions, I mean Sit/Cheal/debuff/Slow etc.<br>
<br>
So taunting in KC is harder than in velk. (I had a hard time to convince ppl that as general consensus is Velk is a higher lvl zone so harder)<br>
<br>
Well, it shouldn't be surprised that different mobs have different aggro behaviour.<br>
<br>
Now, in PoP days, I am lucky enough to have access to various tiers zones - PoV PoS BoT CoD Factory PoTactic. I notice that Mobs in these zones have different Aggro Sensitivity. <br>
<br>
It is interesting that I have a much easier time holding aggro in BoT than in any other said zones. The hardest time I have is actually PoI, both yard trash and Factory mobs. Mobs are extremely sensitive to high aggro actions which causes Ping Pong a lot.<br>
<br>
Agree or not? Any one else have noticed the same things and in what zones? <br>
<br>
<br>
