<br>
Is it possible that the mobs in BoT don't resist Slow as much?  Or is it possible at that high level that the casters more often are wealthy enough to have horses?<br>
<br>
In the Factory in PoI both CHer and Slower had horses and I did not really have issues with keeping Aggro.  THey are also very good at playing their chars, so that may have an effect on the phenomina you are seeing.  <br>
